flowchart LR
    REQ[API Request]

    REQ --> CHECK{rate limit check}
    CHECK -->|within quota| ALLOW[process request]
    CHECK -->|exceeded| DENY[429 Too Many Requests\nRetry-After header]

    ALLOW --> RESP[response]
    DENY --> CLIENT[client backs off]
    CLIENT --> REQ

    ALLOW --> DEDUCT[deduct from quota bucket]
    DEDUCT --> REFILL[sliding window refill]
